Description.BulletDescription:
[RAM & Storage] This computer comes with 16GB RAM | 1024GB SSD 
[ Intel Core i5-1240P Processor] It is a mid-range laptop CPU with 12 cores (4 high-performance cores or P-Cores and 8 power-efficient cores or E-Cores) and 16 threads using the FCBGA1744 socket. The P-Cores base frequency is 1.7 GHz and their maximum boost frequency is 4.4 GHz (1.2 GHz and 3.3 GHz respectively for the E-Cores). [AMD Ryzen 5 7530U Processor] It is a processor for thin and light laptops based on the Cezanne generation. It is part of the second "Barcelo" refresh in early 2023 and offers 200 MHz higher boost clock for the CPU cores compared to the old Ryzen 5 5625U . It integrates six of the eight cores based on the Zen 3 microarchitecture. The cores are clocked at 2 (guaranteed base clock) to 4.5 GHz (single core boost) and support SMT for a total of 12 threads. The chip is manufactured in 7 nm at TSMC.
[15.6" FHD (1920x1080) Display] 1920 x 1080 resolution showcases your games and HD movies with impressive color and clarity. Antireflective finish reduces eyestrain and widens the field of view.
